---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Arnab Sen is a software engineer at Google working on ads machine learning, writing on distributed systems, CS theory, and math."
  ogImage={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}og/about.png`}
>
  <div class="simple-page">
    <h1>About</h1>
    <p>
      Hi, I'm Arnab. I'm a software engineer (L4) at Google, where I work on ads
      machine learning — mostly conversion modeling, calibration, and recovering
      signal in privacy-restricted spaces for YouTube and Search.
    </p>
    <p>
      I studied Computer Science and Technology at IIEST Shibpur, where I found
      competitive programming first (reaching Expert on Codeforces), then
      Capture the Flag competitions with my CTF team, and eventually open source
      through the Coronasafe Pupilfirst Fellowship, building healthcare software
      used during COVID. I've written more about <a
        href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}blog/my-university-experience`}
        >that whole journey here</a
      >.
    </p>
    <p>
      That open-source itch led me to <a
        href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}blog/summer-of-bitcoin-21`}
        >Summer of Bitcoin</a
      >, where I spent a summer contributing to <a
        href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}blog/introduction-to-bitcoin-script`}
        >Bitcoin Core</a
      >, adding USDT tracepoints and eBPF-based scripts. The next year I <a
        href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}blog/landing-a-google-swe-internship`}
        >interned at Google</a
      > as an SWE, which turned into a return offer, then spent my final year
      building an AI-driven AR/VR toolkit at <a
        href="https://www.gmetri.com/"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer">GMetri</a
      > through the <a
        href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}blog/xros-fellowship`}>XROS Fellowship</a
      >, and crypto wallet firmware at <a
        href="https://www.cypherock.com/"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer">Cypherock</a
      >, before joining Google full-time in 2023.
    </p>
    <p>
      I write about what's happening in the AI and LLM industry, distributed
      systems, and core Computer Science fundamentals — see <a
        href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}writing`}>my writing</a
      > or my <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}resume`}>résumé</a>.
    </p>
    <p>
      Find me on <a
        href="https://github.com/arnabsen1729"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a
      > or <a
        href="https://linkedin.com/in/arnabsen1729"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a
      >.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
